Does anybody have any
medical experience?

43:23.448 --> 43:25.448
- I do. I'm Navy.
I have medic training.

43:25.517 --> 43:26.620
- That'll work.
What about you?

43:26.689 --> 43:27.896
- No training
but I've stitched up

43:27.965 --> 43:29.793
about anything
that can be stitched.

43:29.862 --> 43:32.103
- Unbutton his shirt.
I need his shirt open.

43:32.172 --> 43:33.551
Iodine, just pour it on.

43:33.620 --> 43:35.482
Go, go, go.
Directly on his skin.

43:35.551 --> 43:36.965
Come on, ready.

43:37.034 --> 43:38.137
You all right, John?

43:38.206 --> 43:39.310
- I'm not fucking all right.

43:39.379 --> 43:40.206
- Take that,
that goes across him.

43:40.275 --> 43:41.655
That'll do.

43:41.724 --> 43:43.344
You're gonna be all right.

43:46.448 --> 43:47.586
- [grunts] Damnit.

43:47.655 --> 43:48.758
- Hold still.

43:48.827 --> 43:50.344
All right, you got him?
Hold him tight.

43:50.413 --> 43:53.413
This is gonna hurt like hell
and you cannot move.

43:53.482 --> 43:54.965
- Just fuckin do it.

43:55.034 --> 43:56.586
[grunts]

43:56.655 --> 43:59.172
- Hold him.
Hold him.

43:59.241 --> 44:02.551
- Come on.
[groans]

44:02.620 --> 44:05.103
- Stay still.
Hold him.

44:05.172 --> 44:06.758
Hold him tight.

44:06.827 --> 44:08.137
Okay.

44:08.206 --> 44:09.689
Breathe. All right.

44:09.758 --> 44:10.965
The ulcer's gonna spew
like a geyser.

44:11.034 --> 44:12.482
You gotta get pressure on it.
- Got it.

44:12.551 --> 44:14.931
- You guys ready?
All right.

44:15.000 --> 44:16.000
And...

44:17.793 --> 44:20.034
[groaning]

44:20.103 --> 44:21.034
- Doing great.
Hold still.

44:21.103 --> 44:22.034
There you go.

44:22.103 --> 44:25.689
Get pressure on it.

44:25.758 --> 44:27.206
Let me see, let me see.

44:27.275 --> 44:29.206
Okay, I need you guys
to hold him tight.

44:29.275 --> 44:31.620
All right?

44:34.793 --> 44:36.241
You're doing great, John.

44:46.172 --> 44:48.724
[ helicopter whirring ]

45:30.862 --> 45:32.413
- What a fucking mess.

45:36.379 --> 45:39.172
- Yeah well, the bright side,

45:39.241 --> 45:42.827
you don't have cancer.

45:42.896 --> 45:45.448
Not dying yet.

45:45.517 --> 45:48.275
- Maybe not.

45:48.344 --> 45:52.517
But I've been living like it.
That might be worse.

46:02.620 --> 46:04.758
- So much to undo...

46:04.827 --> 46:06.517
So much to undo.
